
Message Queue based on ZooKeeper
--------------------------------

Objectives
----------

Build a highly avaiable & reliable queue. The main focus is not on perfomance! 

Tree Structure
--------------

<app-prefix OR />/
  /queue
    /priority+message1
    /priority+message2
    ...
  /consumers
    /CONSUMER-UUID
      /status     - ephemeral znode
      /message

